========================================================================
                               OpenDCX
========================================================================

OpenDCX is an open-source C++ library comprising extensions for the 
OpenEXR library and its deep file format. It adds support for per
deep-sample metadata adding subpixel-masks and surface-type flags,
and provides utility functions to manipulate deep pixels with this
metadata.

For more details visit the project's home page:
www.opendcx.org
